note over browser:
browser starts executing js-code
that requests JSON data from server 
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_notes_spa
note over browser:
browser is posting the following JSON:
[{ content: "text of the note", date: "2019-05-25T15:15:59.905Z"}]
end note
server-->browser: 201 created
note over browser:
the javascript add the note to the list
and redraw the whole list
(including the new items)
end note
